<HEADLINE>
CONCEPT CAR DESIGNERS TRY TO CAPTURE CALIFORNIA LIFESTYLE
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By Gregory J. Wilcox  
 c.2000 Los Angeles Daily News  
<TEXT>
