<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-01-08 11:55 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0262 &Cx1f; var-z
u a BC-BRAND-CLAIMS-REVIEW-N     01-08 0536
