<DOCNO> NYT20000108.0177 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-01-08 17:32 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0436 &Cx1f; taf-z
u f BC-NY-COMMERCIAL-REAL-11     01-08 1230
