about ways events in deep space could have contributed to the
origin of life on Earth, and discoveries from a new pair of
orbiting telescopes will dominate the national meeting next week in
Atlanta of 1,600 members of the American Astronomical Society.
(Nesmith, Cox News Service) MOVED Wednesday, Jan. 5.
