'00 Celtics with assistant Lester Conner. 2. Conner played on '92
Warriors for Nelson. Randy Wittman, Cavaliers: 1. Assistant on '94
Mavericks under head coach Quinn Buckner. 2. Buckner played on '81
Bucks for Nelson. Rudy Tomjanovich, Rockets: Coach of '00 Rockets
with assistant Larry Smith. 2. Smith played on '89 Warriors for
Nelson. Pat Riley, Heat: 1. Coached '94 Knicks under GM Ernie
Grunfeld. 2. Grunfeld played on '78 Bucks for Nelson.
</P>
<P>
   3 Gar Heard, Wizards: 1. Assistant with '98 Pistons under head
coach Alvin Gentry. 2. Gentry was an assistant on '91 Clippers
under head coach Mike Schuler. 3. Schuler was an assistant with '86
Bucks under head coach Nelson. Lenny Wilkens, Hawks: 1. Coach of
'00 Hawks with assistant Stan Albeck. 2. Albeck was an assistant on
'96 Nets under head coach Butch Beard. 3. Beard was an assistant on
'97 Mavericks, fired by GM Nelson. Flip Saunders, Timberwolves: 1.
Coach of '00 Timberwolves with assistant Greg Ballard. 2. Ballard
was an assistant on '94 Mavericks under head coach Quinn Buckner.
3. Buckner played on '81 Bucks for Nelson. Tim Floyd, Bulls: 1.
Coach of '00 Bulls with assistant Bill Berry. 2. Berry was
assistant on '95 Rockets with Larry Smith. 3. Smith played on '89
Warriors for Nelson.
</P>
<P>
   4 Larry Brown, Sixers: 1. Coached '94 Pacers '94 with assistant
Gar Heard. 2. Heard was an assistant with '98 Pistons under head
coach Alvin Gentry. 3. Gentry was an assistant on '91 Clippers
under head coach Mike Schuler. 4. Schuler was an assistant with '86
Bucks under head coach Nelson. Larry Bird, Pacers: 1. Coach of '00
Pacers with assistant Dick Harter. 2. Harter was assistant with '93
Knicks under head coach Pat Riley. 3. Riley coached '94 Knicks
under GM Ernie Grunfeld. 4. Grunfeld played on '78 Bucks for
Nelson. Jerry Sloan, Jazz: 1. Coach of '00 Jazz with assistant
Gordon Chiesa. 2. Chiesa was assistant for '97 Celtics under head
coach Rick Pitino. 3. Pitino coaches '00 Celtics with assistant
Lester Conner. 4. Conner played on '92 Warriors for Nelson.
</P>
<P>
   6 Don Casey, Nets: 1. Assistant on '98 Nets under head coach
John Calipari. 2. Calipari is an assistant on '00 Sixers under head
coach Larry Brown. 3. Brown coached '94 Pacers with assistant Gar
Heard. 4. Heard was an assistant with '98 Pistons under head coach
Alvin Gentry. 5. Gentry was an assistant on '91 Clippers under head
coach Mike Schuler. 6. Schuler was an assistant with '86 Bucks
under head coach Nelson.
